title: Ole Degnæs
text: Ole Degnæs (29 June 1877 – 27 May 1943) was a Norwegian sport shooter. He was born in <a href="%C3%85rj%C3%A4ng%20Municipality">Årjäng</a> in <a href="V%C3%A4rmland">Värmland</a>, Sweden. He competed in <a href="Shooting%20at%20the%201912%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20team%20rifle">team rifle</a> at the <a href="1912%20Summer%20Olympics">1912 Summer Olympics</a> in <a href="Stockholm">Stockholm</a>, where Norwegian team placed sixth.
